                                      <h1 class="entry-title single-title" itemprop="headline" rel="bookmark">World On Fire: the Music of Fallout 3</h1>
                  
                </header> 
                <section class="entry-wrapper m-all t-3of3 d-7of7 cf" itemprop="articleBody">
                  <div class="entry-content m-all t-2of3 d-5of7 cf">
                  <h3><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W773ZPJhcVw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fred</a></h3>
<h4>11.08.02017</h4>
<hr />
<p><em>This is part of <a href="https://audioxide.com/themusicofgames/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">a series of articles</a> in which we reflect on video game soundtracks. The pieces examine the musical content of the score and analyse the effects it has on the game.</em></p>
<hr />
